https://quarto.org/docs/get-started/hello/rstudio.html
# Quarto (.qmd)
the yaml, a simple one
---
title: "hello"
format: html or pdf or revealjs (slides)
editor: visual
execute:
  echo: false
---

code chunks similar as rmarkdown but options written in the form
#| label: load-packages
#| message: false
#| fig-width: 5
#| fig-asp: 0.618
#| echo: false
#| fig-alt:
#| fig-cap:
#| tab-cap:

- insert code chunk in visual mode using the keyboard shortcut / (forward slash)
